    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supporter Pack</h2>资料包包括可在单人和多人游戏中使用的档案和车辆定制内容。该DLC是可选版本，其将与面向所有《Delivery INC》玩家的免费更新共同发布。如果你喜欢玩《Delivery INC》，并希望游戏内容有进一步提升，那么<strong>Supporter Pack</strong>再适合你不过了！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >档案定制</h2><u>在多人模式中自定义你的档案:</u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>更改档案名称，<br></li><li>更改档案字体样式，<br></li><li>更改头像。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/c1efc27582cd7d056581090bbd0a2ee6.poster.avif?t=1721316418\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/c1efc27582cd7d056581090bbd0a2ee6.webm?t=1721316418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/c1efc27582cd7d056581090bbd0a2ee6.mp4?t=1721316418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强化车辆定制功能</h2><u>通过选择可更改车辆的整体外观:</u><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>多种皮肤，包括新的未来主义变体，<br></li><li>具有单独可定制颜色的新贴花。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/18375dea9063dfdb35c6622377b6dfbc.poster.avif?t=1721316418\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/18375dea9063dfdb35c6622377b6dfbc.webm?t=1721316418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025980/extras/18375dea9063dfdb35c6622377b6dfbc.mp4?t=1721316418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感谢您的支持</h2>感谢您对《Delivery INC》的支持！我们感谢来自我们社区的持续支持和反馈意见。和你的朋友们一起享受新的合作模式吧。自己经营一家小公司可能并不难，但与人合作的话又会如何呢？合作会顺利吗？或者你会出现竞争心态？无论你的游戏风格如何，我们都希望你在《Delivery INC》新的游戏模式中玩得开心！",
